        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-07-10 14:17:50.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nMike, can you do a commit amend, to include a JIRA ticket with the message?   The guidelines are that each commit is linked to a JIRA ticket.    The JIRA ticket should include the purpose of this work, and any documentation on usage that you find suitable.   Let me know too if you decide to do internal demo that Pam suggested.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "4ec3b4f65cfb9dfc7d5edddaed2cef9fdbacb14d",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 805,
