          "display_name": null,
          "email": "michael.mokry@att.com",
          "username": "mmokry"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2017-07-10 15:20:30.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nPamela, I created a Jira ticket for this user story today.  POLICY-67 can be viewed at this link...\nhttps://jira.onap.org/browse/POLICY-67?filter=-1\n\nThe description provides some information with wiki links provided for the feature level and the user stories that I created to provide a solution for the feature.  It is important to note that this is the first part of the feature, I will be working on enhancing the getDecision API in the current iteration to provide the desired treatment in the details of a \"PERMIT\" response. \n\nPlease let me know when will be a good time for us to meet and I can provide an overview and demo of the feature.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
